Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.12,0:00:02.59,Narration Off,,0,0,0,,{\be10}My name's Conan Edogawa!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:02.59,0:00:05.60,Narration Off,,0,0,0,,{\be10}High school student Shin'ichi was\Nforced to take a drug that shrunk him!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.60,0:00:08.57,Narration Off,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Although smaller, my mind remains\Nthat of a sharp detective!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.57,0:00:11.70,Narration Off,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Today's is a ransom case!\NMoney won't buy love!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.70,0:00:15.30,Narration Off,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Even if the evidence is underwater,\Nthere's always only one truth!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.42,0:02:08.29,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's almost time. Don't push it, now.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.29,0:02:11.23,Radio,,0,0,0,,{\be10}The hostage's safety is the most important.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.80,0:02:16.10,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I can hardly believe this is Mr. Takei's daughter...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.14,0:02:20.97,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hello?!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.97,0:02:22.87,Radio,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Do you have the money?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.87,0:02:24.68,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I do!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.68,0:02:26.25,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Let Naoko go!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.25,0:02:29.04,Radio,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Hold on. I'll let you see her.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.82,0:02:37.82,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The kidnapper's showed up\Nin a minivan, Inspector!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.82,0:02:39.95,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It stopped nearby!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.20,0:02:45.82,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Naoko!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.43,0:02:49.66,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'll bring the money now.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.74,0:02:55.51,Radio,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Wait. There are policemen hiding here.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.51,0:02:58.51,Radio,,0,0,0,,{\be10}The deal is off.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.51,0:03:00.88,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.88,0:03:02.44,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,They're running away!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.98,0:03:05.38,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Let's go!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.26,0:03:51.66,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The car never braked\Nand flew right into the water.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.83,0:03:58.94,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,So you were classmates\Nwith the kidnapped Naoko Takei?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.94,0:04:00.91,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.78,0:04:06.18,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Naoko Takei...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.18,0:04:09.58,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}She always looked so lonely...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.58,0:04:12.92,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}But there's no way she could've survived this...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.53,0:04:23.63,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Inspector!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.63,0:04:26.87,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We couldn't find her body at the river bottom either.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.87,0:04:30.90,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The river runs fast in this area,\Nso she may have been taken downstream...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.90,0:04:32.07,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh no!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.07,0:04:34.84,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What do you mean, her body?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.84,0:04:39.15,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I left everything up to you because\NI thought I could trust the police!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.15,0:04:41.05,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And then you screwed everything up!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.05,0:04:44.78,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Give her back! Give Naoko back!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.69,0:04:53.35,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}If the minivan fell front-first,\Nthen why is only the side window broken?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.99,0:04:56.43,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}A hammer!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.43,0:04:58.49,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Conan! Not again!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.49,0:05:00.27,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Sorry!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.27,0:05:02.57,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You lousy kid!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.57,0:05:05.40,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I can no longer trust the police!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.40,0:05:08.44,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,So I would like you to catch the one responsible.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.44,0:05:10.51,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Understood.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.51,0:05:13.51,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,My secretary Hanai{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r} will give you the details.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.51,0:05:16.08,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'm Akiko Hanai.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.08,0:05:20.22,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Could you explain the circumstances\Nunder which she was kidnapped?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.22,0:05:23.52,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Circumstances?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.52,0:05:26.96,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Naoko{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-chan{\r} and I were supposed to see a movie that day,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.96,0:05:29.23,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,so I went to meet her.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.23,0:05:33.53,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But hours passed and she never showed up.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.53,0:05:36.80,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,So you grew worried and contacted the police?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.80,0:05:42.04,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No. I realized it was a kidnapping
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.04,0:05:44.41,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,when the kidnapper called my cell phone.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.41,0:05:49.02,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The kidnapper warned you\Nnot to tell the police, I assume?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.02,0:05:52.18,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I immediately told Mr. Takei...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.18,0:05:58.06,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It was all my fault. If only I hadn't suggested seeing a movie!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.06,0:05:59.73,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ran.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.73,0:06:02.63,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Do you have any ideas about who the kidnapper may be?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.63,0:06:05.63,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I wouldn't have hired you if I did!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.63,0:06:07.93,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Then let me put it another way.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.93,0:06:11.97,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Do you know anyone who may hold a grudge against you?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.97,0:06:15.51,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Pardon my rudeness, but you are an infamous corporate raider.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.51,0:06:18.24,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Are you sure you haven't made a lot of enemies in your time?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.24,0:06:20.65,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}The old man's finally getting better at this!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.65,0:06:23.05,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I don't remember every single thing!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.05,0:06:25.65,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Listen! Business is war!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.65,0:06:27.39,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The losers are the ones at fault!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.39,0:06:29.29,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Got that?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.29,0:06:32.53,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Ugh! He backs down too easy!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.53,0:06:36.33,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Akiko{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}'s room was on the second floor, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.33,0:06:38.00,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Well? How's Akiko{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.00,0:06:39.73,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Dad...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.73,0:06:44.67,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Naoko really thought of Akiko{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r} as an older sister.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.67,0:06:46.94,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,She said that she was also like a mother to her,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.94,0:06:50.14,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,since her real mother had died when she was young.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.38,0:06:53.58,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Akiko{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.58,0:06:55.41,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Akiko{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.85,0:06:59.37,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.02,0:07:03.19,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh, it's you two...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.19,0:07:06.69,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Are you alright? We called out to you a couple times...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.69,0:07:11.30,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry. I damaged my hearing a bit...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.30,0:07:13.57,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Huh? She's—
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.57,0:07:16.57,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Have you given up on Naoko{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-chan{\r} too?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.57,0:07:20.63,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,She's alive! I just know it!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.98,0:07:29.72,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But they've looked this hard\Nand still haven't found her...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.72,0:07:31.58,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,She's probably—
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.79,0:07:40.73,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That poor woman...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.53,0:07:44.66,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}That's it!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.66,0:07:47.60,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ran{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-neechan{\r}! Let's take a look over there!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.60,0:07:49.17,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What for?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.17,0:07:52.23,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Somebody might've seen it!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.41,0:07:55.84,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That day?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.84,0:07:58.21,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Did anything out of the ordinary happen?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.21,0:08:02.38,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You can say that. The police asked us to help with their investigation.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.38,0:08:05.38,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,All the ships in this area helped 'em.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.38,0:08:06.55,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,All of them?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.55,0:08:12.19,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah. It's the sailors' code to work together when something happens.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.19,0:08:16.36,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Not that guy with the speedboat, though...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.36,0:08:17.63,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Speedboat?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.63,0:08:22.76,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah, it almost ran straight into my boat, here...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.21,0:08:33.71,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Probably some rich guy who goes around sailing with other rich guys.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.71,0:08:36.94,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What kind of speedboat was it?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.25,0:08:42.79,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Is this the speedboat he was talking about?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.79,0:08:48.16,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Conan{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r}! Don't get on without permission!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.16,0:08:50.73,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Diving equipment?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.73,0:08:55.19,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Both the kidnapper and\NNaoko Takei may still be alive!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.84,0:09:03.81,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}That was no accident—\Nthe kidnapper drove off on purpose.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.81,0:09:05.94,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}As a means of escape!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.69,0:09:20.86,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}The kidnapper broke the side window with a hammer
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.86,0:09:23.50,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}that was placed in the car in advance,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.50,0:09:26.83,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}swam underwater to the opposite shore,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.83,0:09:29.53,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}and got into a waiting speedboat!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.44,0:09:35.37,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}The culprit then escaped
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.37,0:09:38.24,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}while the police were focusing their attention on the minivan.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.38,0:09:42.58,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Why would they do that?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.58,0:09:45.55,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Probably to confuse the police into thinking
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.55,0:09:51.49,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}that both kidnapper and the hostage had died.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.49,0:09:53.32,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}There could be other reasons, too...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.66,0:10:02.10,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}The only thing I don't understand is about the hostage, Naoko Takei.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.10,0:10:04.24,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Her body hasn't turned up.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.24,0:10:08.07,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}We only found enough scuba diving equipment for one person.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.07,0:10:11.81,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}How did the kidnapper get her out of the sunken car?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.81,0:10:15.68,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Or was she never in it at all?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.48,0:10:21.69,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}No, she was seen inside it!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.69,0:10:24.22,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Conan{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r}!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.22,0:10:27.16,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ran{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-neechan{\r}! Did you find anything out?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.16,0:10:29.03,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,According to the manager here,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.03,0:10:33.90,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,the boat's owner simply abandoned it\Nand it hasn't been used since.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.90,0:10:37.04,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Maybe that man mistook it for another boat...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.04,0:10:39.04,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}That can't be!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.04,0:10:41.94,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}But how do I prove this!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.78,0:10:44.88,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The investigation is canceled?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.88,0:10:47.18,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What for? What's going on?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.18,0:10:51.25,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Don't look at me. He was the one who decided to cancel it!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.25,0:10:53.32,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'd like to know why, myself!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.32,0:10:56.32,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Rich people are stingy, after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.32,0:11:00.69,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He probably regrets wasting money\Non his dead daughter now.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.69,0:11:03.93,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No! She's not dead at all!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.93,0:11:06.73,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And how do you know that?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.73,0:11:08.37,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Um, well...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.37,0:11:09.94,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I think so too!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.94,0:11:14.57,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I don't want to believe that Naoko's dead!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.57,0:11:19.01,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ugh. Kids can be so pampered sometimes.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.01,0:11:23.28,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Listen. It's obvious once you think about it with a cool head.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.28,0:11:24.85,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Given the circumstances,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.85,0:11:29.29,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,neither the hostage nor the kidnapper can possibly be alive.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.29,0:11:31.02,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.02,0:11:32.06,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But you know,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.06,0:11:36.96,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,by doing this, he's basically insulting your reputation as a great detective.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.96,0:11:39.30,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You have a point there!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.30,0:11:40.99,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Alright, then!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.40,0:11:44.84,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Leave!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.84,0:11:48.77,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,My daughter—Naoko—is dead!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.77,0:11:51.71,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,There's no bringing her back now!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.71,0:11:53.70,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.28,0:12:00.62,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,This is what you want, isn't it?!\NYour cancellation fee.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.62,0:12:04.46,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Take it and get out!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.46,0:12:08.63,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I don't want your lousy money! You can keep it!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.63,0:12:10.75,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ran! Let's go!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.00,0:12:19.84,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Damn it! That old fogy really knows how to piss me off!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.84,0:12:22.80,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh, I just remembered...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.80,0:12:23.84,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.84,0:12:26.88,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I promised to meet my friends...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.88,0:12:27.41,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,See ya!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.41,0:12:30.97,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Bah. That spoiled little kid has it easy.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.95,0:12:38.26,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}His attitude changed too quickly!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.26,0:12:39.85,Flashback,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Leave!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.83,0:12:46.09,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}There's no mistake about it!\NThe kidnapper must've contacted him!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.83,0:12:58.82,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Are you just going to let Naoko{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-chan{\r} die?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.70,0:13:02.50,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Mr. Takei!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.50,0:13:05.47,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,If you don't really gather all the money this time,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.47,0:13:08.61,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,she might be killed!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.61,0:13:11.74,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But we don't even know if she's alive or not—
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.74,0:13:14.71,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Mr. Takei! Have a look for yourself!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.81,0:13:18.42,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Even in the picture the kidnapper sent us,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.42,0:13:22.18,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,the newspaper has yesterday's date!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.95,0:13:25.82,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}I thought so.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.49,0:13:35.80,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Naoko{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-chan{\r} believes with all her heart that you'll save her!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.80,0:13:37.13,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Mr. Takei!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.13,0:13:40.57,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,If I gather the 500 million now and then lose it in another stupid mistake,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.57,0:13:44.91,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,my latest business deal will go up in smoke!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.91,0:13:46.77,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Don't you see?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.38,0:13:52.25,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Money or Naoko{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-chan{\r}? Which is more important?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.25,0:13:53.95,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Naoko, of course!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.95,0:13:58.05,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But if this deal falls through, my company will go—
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.05,0:14:01.93,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,—bankrupt. There's no question about that.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.93,0:14:04.63,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Who cares about the company?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.63,0:14:07.13,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It won't replace Naoko{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-chan{\r}'s life!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.13,0:14:12.20,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But I built this company with my own two hands!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.20,0:14:14.37,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah, by sucking the lifeblood out of other people!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.37,0:14:16.21,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Shut up!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.21,0:14:19.47,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Corporate raiding is a perfectly legitimate business!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.88,0:14:24.61,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Weak people lose! And the losers have no one to blame but themselves!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.42,0:14:28.61,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}That damn old man!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.92,0:14:33.96,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Who's there?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.96,0:14:35.19,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Why, you little!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.91,0:14:37.52,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Conan{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r}!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.56,0:14:40.93,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I was looking for the bathroom—
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.93,0:14:43.03,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,This is private property, boy!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.03,0:14:47.10,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Please don't tell anyone about this, Conan{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r}.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.10,0:14:52.04,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,If the police found out, Naoko{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-chan{\r} would be killed for sure this time!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.04,0:14:55.38,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.38,0:14:58.11,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We can't afford to let him leave here for a while!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.11,0:15:00.81,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Lock him in your room or something!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.69,0:15:07.82,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Sorry about this, Conan{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r}.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.82,0:15:10.16,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Try to endure it for a short while.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.16,0:15:13.63,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Once the deal is over, I promise we'll let you out.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.63,0:15:16.27,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Say, what did the kidnapper tell you guys?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.27,0:15:17.60,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The same as before.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.60,0:15:20.70,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,"Prepare 500 million yen by tomorrow."
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.70,0:15:23.07,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Are you going to pay?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.07,0:15:25.88,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You saw what kind of person Mr. Takei is...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.88,0:15:29.88,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He'll get the money if Naoko{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r} is important to him, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.88,0:15:33.68,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Money is the only thing important to him!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.79,0:15:40.66,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.66,0:15:43.66,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I had a younger brother named Masahito.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.66,0:15:44.89,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,"Had"?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.89,0:15:48.56,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yes. He died, four years ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.43,0:15:52.67,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No, he was murdered.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.67,0:15:55.30,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He was still about your age.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.24,0:16:01.23,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry. Let me hold you for a while.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.59,0:16:14.35,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'll bring some dinner later.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.74,0:16:35.28,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Do you think you can fool the kidnapper
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.28,0:16:38.21,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,with these wads of cash made out of newspaper?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.21,0:16:42.05,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Quiet. This is the only choice left!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.50,0:16:53.66,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Conan{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r}!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.66,0:16:56.26,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What are you doing?! Let's go!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.46,0:17:21.52,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Now that I think about it,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.52,0:17:25.03,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}nobody's actually seen Naoko Takei's face!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.03,0:17:27.03,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Her mouth was taped and she had a blindfold on...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.03,0:17:29.80,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}...there was no way to see her face clearly!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.80,0:17:33.27,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}The kidnapper was the only person\Never inside the minivan!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.27,0:17:36.30,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Yes! One person played the role of two!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.27,0:17:40.88,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Nobody once doubted that it was Naoko.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.88,0:17:43.08,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}It's not unreasonable—she was far away,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.08,0:17:46.17,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}and everyone just assumed it was her.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.89,0:17:54.76,Flashback,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Wait. There are policemen hiding here.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.76,0:17:56.96,Flashback,,0,0,0,,{\be10}The deal is off.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.96,0:18:00.10,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}The kidnapper was completely aware\Nof what the police were up to!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.10,0:18:01.66,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}It's only natural!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.66,0:18:04.79,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}The kidnapper was always right by Takei{\rHonorifics - Thoughts\be10}-san{\r\be10}, after all!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.24,0:18:14.78,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}The diving watch mark on her arm...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.78,0:18:16.91,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Her tan line from wearing a wetsuit...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.91,0:18:20.45,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}And then what she did that one time!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.45,0:18:23.59,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}An ear-unplugging technique\Nthat every diver knows about!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.59,0:18:28.89,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}She must've injured her ears\Nwhen she suddenly entered the water!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.83,0:18:33.63,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What's going on?! It's long past our agreed time!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.63,0:18:36.69,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The kidnapper is here. Has been for a while.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.74,0:18:42.41,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What are you doing, you idiot?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.41,0:18:44.87,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You made me sprain my ankle!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.87,0:18:47.18,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.18,0:18:50.65,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Compared to the pain\Nyou gave my family, anyway.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.65,0:18:52.28,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Come again?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.28,0:18:55.25,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You don't remember this place?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.89,0:19:00.09,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,These are the remains of a company that you took hostile control over.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.09,0:19:02.09,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What?! You don't mean that you're—
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.09,0:19:03.93,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's right!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.93,0:19:08.00,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'm the daughter of the former company director here.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.00,0:19:13.57,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,My father killed himself, and he took his wife and son with him...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.57,0:19:16.17,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Leaving only me behind...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.17,0:19:18.31,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I was a college student at the time.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.31,0:19:22.11,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I was taken in by some relatives, changed my last name,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.11,0:19:25.48,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,and then joined your company.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.48,0:19:28.28,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,To wait for a chance to get revenge, of course.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.82,0:19:33.62,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,If you had loved Naoko{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-chan{\r} enough to simply get the money ready,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.62,0:19:35.72,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I had intended to let you live!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.96,0:19:42.87,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What are you planning to do?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.87,0:19:45.16,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Have you die.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.08,0:19:53.74,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Gasoline?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.74,0:19:55.40,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}This is bad!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.25,0:20:01.12,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Wait, I apologize! I'll pay as much as you want!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.12,0:20:02.92,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Just don't do it!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.92,0:20:06.12,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Take your money with you to hell.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.36,0:20:08.59,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Farewell.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.59,0:20:10.75,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No! Don't do it!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.36,0:20:14.93,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Conan{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r}!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.93,0:20:17.23,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,There's no value in killing that man!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.23,0:20:19.14,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,There's no value in letting him live!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.14,0:20:20.67,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's my duty to rid the world of him!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.67,0:20:24.37,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Do you want Naoko{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r} to think the same way about you?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.44,0:20:29.61,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That man is her only family!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.55,0:20:35.85,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You should know more than anyone else
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.85,0:20:38.88,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,the pain of having your entire family die!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.46,0:20:46.19,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Even if you did get revenge, I don't think your brother would be happy.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.48,0:21:02.41,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Conan{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r}...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.92,0:21:07.94,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Masahito...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:53.79,0:22:58.29,Narration Off,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Naoko Takei was being held in the basement of the old factory.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:58.29,0:23:00.36,Narration Off,,0,0,0,,{\be10}She was rescued safely.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:00.36,0:23:03.37,Narration Off,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Apparently, she was somewhat aware of the situation
Dialogue: 0,0:23:03.37,0:23:07.07,Narration Off,,0,0,0,,{\be10}when she was first confined.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:07.07,0:23:10.14,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Naoko! You're safe!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.14,0:23:11.97,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Akiko{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:13.84,0:23:15.61,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Akiko{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:18.61,0:23:22.55,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'm so sorry I got you involved, Naoko{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-chan{\r}.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.79,0:23:27.55,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Thank you!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:54.50,0:23:56.10,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We still can't say anything for sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:56.10,0:24:00.34,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,If he really attacked for no reason as she says,
Dialogue: 0,0:24:00.34,0:24:03.28,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,then he'll probably have to be put to sleep.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:03.28,0:24:07.51,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Please come back, Shin'ichi...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:07.51,0:24:10.78,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}You're the only one who can save John!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:11.03,0:24:16.99,Signs,,0,0,0,,Next Conan:
Dialogue: 0,0:24:16.99,0:24:22.00,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Next Conan's Hint: Conditioned reflex
Dialogue: 0,0:24:16.99,0:24:22.00,Signs,,0,0,0,,Conditioned reflex
Dialogue: 0,0:24:22.70,0:24:23.60,Dialogue Top,,0,0,0,,Next time...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:23.60,0:24:25.67,Dialogue Top,,0,0,0,,John, dinnertime! Stay...
